ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.
M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: For each of the following statements, please indicate how you feel about the support you have right now: I have good friends who support me.
Notes: 0=Not applicable; 1=Never; 2=Rarely; 3=Some of the time; 4=Most of the time; 5=Always; -99=Skipped or left unanswered

ElementDescription: For each of the following statements, please indicate how you feel about the support you have right now: My family is always there for me.
Notes: 0=Not applicable; 1=Never; 2=Rarely; 3=Some of the time; 4=Most of the time; 5=Always; -99=Skipped or left unanswered

ElementDescription: For each of the following statements, please indicate how you feel about the support you have right now: My husband/partner helps me a lot.
Notes: 0=Not applicable; 1=Never; 2=Rarely; 3=Some of the time; 4=Most of the time; 5=Always; -99=Skipped or left unanswered

ElementDescription: For each of the following statements, please indicate how you feel about the support you have right now: There is conflict with my husband/partner.
Notes: Item is reverse-scored. 0=Not applicable; 1=Always; 2=Most of the time; 3=Some of the time; 4=Rarely; 5=Never; -99=Skipped or left unanswered

ElementDescription: For each of the following statements, please indicate how you feel about the support you have right now: I feel controlled by my husband/partner.
Notes: Item is reverse-scored. 0=Not applicable; 1=Always; 2=Most of the time; 3=Some of the time; 4=Rarely; 5=Never; -99=Skipped or left unanswered

ElementDescription: For each of the following statements, please indicate how you feel about the support you have right now: I feel loved by my husband/partner.
Notes: 0=Not applicable; 1=Never; 2=Rarely; 3=Some of the time; 4=Most of the time; 5=Always; -99=Skipped or left unanswered

ElementDescription: Maternity Social Support Scale (MSSS) total score
Notes: Sum: msss_a, msss_b, msss_c, msss_d, msss_e, msss_f; -99=Skipped or left unanswered
